    <h1>Operators</h1><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_arithmetic_operators">Arithmetic operators</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Do you remember elementary arithmetics from school? Arithmetic operators allow you to perform elementary arithmetics and additional calculations.</p>
</div>
